u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng \u00e2m, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7t l\u01b0\u1ee1i, b\u1eadt h\u01a1i, m\u1edf kh\u1ea9u h\u00ecnh mi\u1ec7ng,\u2026 cho t\u1eebng \u00e2m ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7i ph\u00e1t \u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam hay g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i h\u1ecdc ph\u00e1t \u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u n\u1eefa, y\u00ean t\u00e2m t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Hack N\u00e3o th\u00f4i.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-540271672\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner text-center\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<a class=\"button secondary is-large lowercase reveal-icon nut-xem-tat-ca\"  style=\"border-radius:99px;\">\n  <i class=\"icon-shopping-cart\" ><\/i>  <span>M\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1eb7t mua cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_654007047 {\n  padding-top: 70px;\n  padding-bottom: 70px;\n  background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t<section class=\"section tac-gia-section\" id=\"section_163200473\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1595095613\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-957411760\" class=\"col medium-8 small-12 large-8\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<h2>T\u00c1C GI\u1ea2 CU\u1ed0N S\u00c1CH L\u00c0 AI?<\/h2>\n<p>\u201cKhi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n, lu\u00f4n ao \u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eddi t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i B\u00e1nh m\u1ef3 gi\u00fap tr\u00ed nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a Doraemon ho\u1eb7c m\u00ecnh sinh ra \u1edf c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee1 ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh. Qua m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, ho\u00e1 ra vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00fang.<\/p>\n<p>K\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0y x\u01b0a c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 117 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 qu\u00ean 8 t\u1eeb sau 1 tu\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfng Anh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201ckh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef\u201d c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 d\u00e2n h\u1ecdc chuy\u00ean. Tin m\u00ecnh \u0111i. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3>NGUY\u1ec4N HI\u1ec6P<\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">Ch\u1ee7 bi\u00ean 2 cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t TIKI 2018:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u201cHack N\u00e3o 1500 t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng Anh\u201d <\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u201cV\u1eeba l\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba b\u1eadn v\u1eabn gi\u1ecfi ti\u1ebfng Anh\u201d<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-452421238\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_225976419\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img width=\"423\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Asset-16.png\" class=\"attachment-original size-original\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Asset-16.png 423w, https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Asset-16-220x300.png 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_225976419 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_163200473 {\n  padding-top: 64px;\n  padding-bottom: 64px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t<section class=\"section banner1 thong-bao dark\" id=\"section_50572736\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"max-width:900px\" id=\"row-1532898172\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-729041783\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner text-center\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"container section-title-container\" ><h3 class=\"section-title section-title-center\"><b><\/b><span class=\"section-title-main\" style=\"font-size:115%;\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c s\u00e1ch<\/span><b><\/b><\/h3><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_1068177212\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img width=\"519\" height=\"369\" src=\"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/\u0110\u1ed4I-S\u00c1CH.png\" class=\"attachment-original size-original\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/\u0110\u1ed4I-S\u00c1CH.png 519w, https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/\u0110\u1ed4I-S\u00c1CH-300x213.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 519px) 100vw, 519px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_1068177212 {\n  width: 74%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_29 et_pb_bg_layout_lightet_pb_text_align_justified\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n<div id=\"element-295\" class=\"widget item-absolute headline\" data-at=\"headline\">\n<div class=\"contents\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><i>\u201cD\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 thanh xu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean Hack N\u00e3o 1500 t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh, t\u1ea1i sao Step Up n\u1ee1 l\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?\u201d<\/i><\/strong><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"element-298\" class=\"widget item-absolute headline\" data-at=\"headline\">\n<div class=\"contents\">\n<p class=\"x_9174794d\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><em><span class=\"x_f2074b6c\">V\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean g\u00f3p \u00fd, ch\u00fang m\u00ecnh l\u1eafng nghe. M\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau khi ra m\u1eaft phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, Step Up quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft tay bi\u00ean so\u1ea1n Phi\u00ean B\u1ea3n 2019 \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n mang t\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"x_9174794d\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><em><span class=\"x_f2074b6c\">Step Up th\u00e2n b\u00e1o th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u2013 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch \u2013 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ai b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o m\u1edbi n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p class=\"x_9174794d\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><em><span class=\"x_f2074b6c\">Step Up ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Hack N\u00e3o 1500 t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh (2019) v\u00e0 s\u1edbm gi\u1ecfi ti\u1ebfng Anh!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_50572736 {\n  padding-top: 49px;\n  padding-bottom: 49px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n\t<section class=\"section chinh-sach-section\" id=\"section_1771203238\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded\" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-154210473\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1207545972\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"container section-title-container\" ><h2 class=\"section-title section-title-center\"><b><\/b><span class=\"section-title-main\" style=\"font-size:95%;color:rgb(0, 64, 0);\">Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/span><b><\/b><\/h2><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-476994778\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" style=\"width: 60px\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-inner\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"81\" height=\"81\" src=\"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/Asset-20.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-text last-reset\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h4>CHI\u1ebeN BINH STEP UP H\u1ed6 TR\u1ee2 B\u1ea0N \u0110\u1ebeN TRANG CU\u1ed0I C\u00d9NG<\/h4>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh hay n\u1ed9i dung cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch, Step Up s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1ecdi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi. Step Up \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ebfn trang cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\t<div class=\"icon-box featured-box icon-box-left text-left\"  >\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon-box-img\" styl