\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1512410665\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<h3><span style=\"color: #003800;\"><strong>T\u1ea1i sao cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfng Anh \u0111\u1eaft th\u1ebf?<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>S\u00e1ch Hack N\u00e3o 1500 t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in m\u00e0u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u gi\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng, kh\u1ed5 A4, d\u00e0y g\u1ea7n 500 trang. B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 g\u1ed3m 25 cu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec7n tranh, v\u1eeba gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng trung c\u1ea5p, l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #003800;\"><b>Ch\u1ec9 h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb th\u00f4i c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng v\u00e0o n\u00f3i v\u00e0 vi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>S\u00e1ch g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 t\u1eeb v\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u00f3 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 minh h\u1ecda v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 audio\u2026 b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n y\u00ean t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 8 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p v\u00e0\u00a0c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o n\u00f3i v\u00e0 vi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-370111507\" class=\"col medium-6 small-12 large-6\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_42 et_pb_bg_layout_lightet_pb_text_align_justified\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n<h3><span style=\"color: #003800;\"><b>S\u00e1ch to, d\u00e0y th\u1ebf h\u1ecdc bao gi\u1edd m\u1edbi h\u1ebft?<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ea1n y\u00ean t\u00e2m, 50% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 tranh v\u1ebd \u0111an xen. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung c\u00e1c c\u00e2u truy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e2u \u00e2m thanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_43 et_pb_bg_layout_lightet_pb_text_align_justified\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n<h3><span style=\"color: #003800;\"><b>H\u1ecdc qua \u00c2m thanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u00f3 h\u1ecfng ph\u00e1t \u00e2m kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng nh\u00e9, s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i k\u00e8m ph\u1ea7n t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m thanh cho m\u1ed7i t\u1eeb v\u00e0 n\u00e3o b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd l\u01b0u gi\u1eef \u00e2m thanh n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n ph\u1ea7n phi\u00ean \u00e2m ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u201cc\u1ea7u t\u1ea1m\u201d cho t\u1edbi khi t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0u trong tr\u00ed nh\u1edb d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n\u00a0s\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfng Anh\u00a0n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ee7 8 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ee9 y\u00ean t\u00e2m h\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_580609617 {\n  padding-top: 49px;\n  padding-bottom: 49px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/section>\n\t\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"page-blank.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/edu8.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v